1.Write a HTML code to display six different heading elements and that also includes normal paragraph text. Compare the fonts used for the various headings with the default font used for paragraph text.

PROGRAM:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Headings and Paragraph Font Comparison</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    h1 {
        font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    }
    h2 {
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    h3 {
        font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
    }
    h4 {
        font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;
    }
    h5 {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    h6 {
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", sans-serif;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>This is a Heading 1</h1>
    <h2>This is a Heading 2</h2>
    <h3>This is a Heading 3</h3>
    <h4>This is a Heading 4</h4>
    <h5>This is a Heading 5</h5>
    <h6>This is a Heading 6</h6>
    
    <p>This is a normal paragraph text. The font used for this paragraph is the default font specified in the body CSS rule (Arial, sans-serif).</p>
</body>
</html>



2.Create "Italian Flag" (given below) using CSS box model with the following condition.
    1. Create a div with height of 400px, width of 80 pixels, and a green background.
    2. Beneath that, create a div with the same dimensions and white background.
    3. Beneath that, create another div with the same dimensions and red.

PROGRAM:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Italian Flag</title>
<style>
    .flag-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .flag-color {
        height: 400px;
        width: 80px;
    }

    .green {
        background-color: green;
    }

    .white {
        background-color: white;
    }

    .red {
        background-color: red;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="flag-container">
        <div class="flag-color green"></div>
        <div class="flag-color white"></div>
        <div class="flag-color red"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

